Invocation Name: ecolane transit connect
des:
Use Alexa to connect to your local transit agency through Ecolane Transit Connect. You will be able to book a trip, get details about upcoming trips, and more.

When installing this skill, you will be prompted to link your Alexa account to an already created transit agency account.
